-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://appzapper.com/


Torrent uploaded by Zeus-Downloads Team
-------------------------------------------


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "AppZapper v2.0.1.dmg"
- Drag/Copy "AppZapper.app" to your "Applications" folder.
- Open "AppZapper.app", a "Registration" window will come up.
- Open "Name and License.txt" and copy the license informations.
- Paste them to AppZapper and then click on "Register".
- Congratulations, you now have a fully functional copy of AppZapper.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update AppZapper as updating it might cause a problem. You have been warned.
